272
00:19:14,445 --> 00:19:16,697
<i>Kedipan kecil itu bukan asteroid.</i>

273
00:19:16,698 --> 00:19:18,657
<i>Itu pesawat luar angkasa,
dan sedang membuntuti kita.</i>

274
00:19:18,658 --> 00:19:21,076
<i>- Semakin dekat.</i>
- <i>Mustahil, Rigna.</i>

275
00:19:21,077 --> 00:19:23,745
<i>Mereka tak mungkin mendeteksi kita.
